TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT A.FRMLY_PROD_GID, B.FRMLY_ID, B.FRMLY_BUILD_TYP_CD, B.FRMLY_EFF_DT, B.FRMLY_EXPRN_DT, B.FRMLY_NM, A.FRMLY_TIER_STRATG_ID, A.FRMLY_SEQ_NBR, A.TIER_EFF_DT, A.TIER_EXPRN_DT, A.TIER_STRATG_DESC, A.TIER_STRATG_DTL_SEQ_NBR, A.SRC_CHG_TS, A.SRC_CD FROM DWU_CLIN.V_FRMLY_TIER_STRATG_DTL_HIST A, DWU_CLIN.V_FRMLY_HIST B WHERE A.FRMLY_PROD_GID= B.FRMLY_PROD_GID ORDER BY B.FRMLY_BUILD_TYP_CD, B.FRMLY_ID, A.FRMLY_TIER_STRATG_ID, A.TIER_STRATG_DTL_SEQ_NBR, A.TIER_EFF_DT

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: ITPR007923 Aetna Coventry Project (08/28/2014): Check if source row exist in target table 1) If the record is present, then compare the column values of source and target. If there is a difference then set CHANGE_FLAG = 1 to denote it as changed record else CHANGE_FLAG = 0 2) If the record isn't present then set NEW_FLAG=1 to denote as new record.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_SCD_RECS

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: Housekeeping field (Create Timestamp)

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: This flags 1 for the record if it is found to be a New Record. (i.e if the record exists in source but doesnot exist in GDX target table)
TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(ISNULL(Tgt_FRMLY_PROD_GID) AND ISNULL(Tgt_FRMLY_SEQ_NBR) AND ISNULL(Tgt_FRMLY_TIER_STRATG_ID) AND ISNULL(Tgt_TIER_STRATG_DTL_SEQ_NBR) AND ISNULL(Tgt_TIER_EFF_DT),1,0)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: NEW_FLAG

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: This flags 1 for the record if it is found to be a changed record. (i.e if the record exists in source and target but atleast one of non PK fields differ in their values in Source and GDX target table)
TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(NOT ISNULL(Tgt_FRMLY_PROD_GID) AND NOT ISNULL(Tgt_FRMLY_SEQ_NBR) AND NOT ISNULL(Tgt_FRMLY_TIER_STRATG_ID) AND NOT ISNULL(Tgt_TIER_STRATG_DTL_SEQ_NBR) AND NOT ISNULL(Tgt_TIER_EFF_DT) AND (LTRIM(RTRIM(Tgt_FRMLY_ID))!= LTRIM(RTRIM(Src_FRMLY_ID)) OR LTRIM(RTRIM(Tgt_FRMLY_SRC_CD))!= LTRIM(RTRIM(Src_FRMLY_SRC_CD)) OR Tgt_FRMLY_EFF_DT!= Src_FRMLY_EFF_DT OR Tgt_FRMLY_EXPRN_DT!= Src_FRMLY_EXPRN_DT OR LTRIM(RTRIM(Tgt_FRMLY_NM))!= LTRIM(RTRIM(Src_FRMLY_NM)) OR Tgt_TIER_EXPRN_DT!= Src_TIER_EXPRN_DT OR Tgt_EFF_DT!= Src_EFF_DT OR Tgt_END_DT!= Src_END_DT OR LTRIM(RTRIM(Tgt_TIER_STRATG_DESC))!= LTRIM(RTRIM(Src_TIER_STRATG_DESC)) OR Tgt_SRC_CHG_TS!= Src_SRC_CHG_TS OR LTRIM(RTRIM(Tgt_SRC_CD))!= LTRIM(RTRIM(Src_SRC_CD))),1, 0 )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: CHANGED_FLAG
